# kitconcept.contactblock

Contact block by kitconcept

## Features

* Serializer used by the Contact Block

## Installation

Install kitconcept.contactblock with uv.

```shell
uv add kitconcept.contactblock
```

Create the Plone site.

```shell
make create-site
```

